Kutfutfukisa iManuwali lesebentisekako yeSibonelo seTetimali neluHlelo lwekuSita letawusita bohulumende basemakhaya uma bahlatiya kusimama kutetimali kwaletindlela letehlukene tekuphakelwa kwetinsita temanti amahhala lasisekelo.
Lesibonelo sitawuphindze sisite bomasipala ekuhloleni kutsi ngabe inchubomgomo yekuphakelwa kwemanti amahhala lasisekelo ingentiwa njani kutsi ibe ngulenekusimama kutetimali ngekulandzela tingucuko latiba khona kusakhiwo sematharifi kanye nekutsi ngabe nguyiphi inhlanganisela yemitfombo yemalingena lefaneleke kakhulu kulowo nalowo masipala lotsintsekako.
